text: Domburg-Binnen is a former municipality in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It existed until 1816, when it merged with Domburg-Buiten to form the new municipality of Domburg.Ad van der Meer and Onno Boonstra, "Repertorium van Nederlandse gemeenten", KNAW, 2006. The municipality of Domburg-Binnen covered the city of Domburg itself, and a few of the surrounding dunes. ==References== Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Veere
